Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing! I'm definitely\Ngonna wear a scarf tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gets pretty cold in the evenings now, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Don't you go\Nstealing {\i1}my {\i0}Miyamura, Tanihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not stealing him from you, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are so weird! You're always\Ncuddling with each other and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've kinda gotten close lately, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell do you mean, you've gotten close?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Closer than {\i1}just friends{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. I'm not Shindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.09,0:01:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that\Nwhat Shindo-kun is to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Tanihara, spill the damn beans!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, I saw Shindo go over to\NMiyamura's to get a change of clothes once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, he stays over at my place a lot!\NEven when I don't want him to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wild Shindo appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why're you guys blockin' the\Nsidewalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's goin' on, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shindo-kun, are you close with Chika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kinda? Though lately,\Nshe's been busy studying for exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we haven't hung out much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I've spent plenty\Nof nights at Miyamura's!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shindo, let's go get some Mickey D's!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't spell "burger"\Nwithout Shindo, am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Makes no sense, but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that free coffee coupon still good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miyamura, I just want you\Nto know something, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about {\i1}girls{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I think about\Nsome {\i1}guy {\i0}taking you, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking me {\i1}how{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you fall for\Nsomeone else, it better be a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No guys, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I had to promise her "no guys" yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys need to stay away from me, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what about when\Nyou need to use the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck with that, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, this is my day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've gone shopping\Nfor art supplies by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to hit up the bookstore, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't carry everything by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or you could just go to\Nthe bookstore another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Yoshikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yanagi-kun? Whoa, you're wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was you. What're you shopping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, books and stuff, but mostly art supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Art supplies? I didn't know you\Nwere an artist, Yoshikawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're not for me, they're for my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you, I'm Akane Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likewise. Didn't know Yuki was\Nfriends with a hottie like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless you're her {\i1}boyfriend{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, ma'am. She turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured. You wouldn't date--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, she turned you down?!\NNot the other way around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm far out of her league.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Yuki's league? {\i1}This {\i0}Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can stop looking at me like that!\NI hear you loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my sister's such an ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This was a pleasant surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never imagined being able\Nto speak to you outside of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I shouldn't say that,\Nor Ishikawa-kun will get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he wouldn't. You're a good guy, Yanagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tooru wouldn't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear those two are dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, really? I thought so!\NThey {\i1}are {\i0}always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They make a good couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that Kono-san is totally fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fooled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kono-san thinks Tooru and I are dating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does she? I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She sorta asked me about it today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I told her we were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't I just tell her the truth?\NWhat's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you want to talk to me\Nto see if I'd tell her the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll stay quiet about it if you admit\Nthat you have a crush on Ishikawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's not fair about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one being unfair, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lied to Kono-san, knowing it would hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen someone's lips\Ntremble like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know this won't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Tooru doesn't like me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should've stopped\Npretending that very same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he holds my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's nice to me, even when I don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I asked you to keep up\Nthe act for a while, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep pretending, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I just want this lie of ours\Nto become something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would never be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki was out today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many days is that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three? Four? I think she's been out all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'd text us back if she were sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop spacing out! We're talking about Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten any texts\Nback from Yoshikawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, she's not texting me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's dealing with family stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should probably tell her the test\Nis gonna cover different stuff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How funny would it be if she\Nthrew a tantrum over the test stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno if she'd throw a whole {\i1}tantrum{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope she comes tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you need to go to school already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you worried about your attendance record?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This girl called Hori-san called.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said you turned off your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme guess, you want something again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any time you want something,\Nyou never say you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea why you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong or embarrassing\Nabout wanting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you need decide\Nif you're going to get it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You always end up\Ncomplaining about it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want a hair clip like hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan, you just said you didn't want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want something, then say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've had this bad habit forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you stopped making those cookies, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That last batch you did was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those pure-white ones, like snow--\Nlike your name. Those were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pure-white, like snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, așa este.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,did I tell you the test's\Ncovering different stuff now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's still all stuff\NI'm crap at, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the end\Nof our little game of pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you wanna talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's freezing up here; let's make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gotta give Hori her notebook back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see my text?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about Kono-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When she told me she liked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me she didn't need an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, she doesn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason she thinks we're dating,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she just wanted to get that off her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell her, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That we're not dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno. I didn't feel like I had\Nto clear up the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I promised you I'd play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you didn't have to pretend,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what would you have told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Kono-san's way out of my league.\NI wouldn't be good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll find someone way better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Î-Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess that means\Nno more {\i1}sakura {\i0}cookies, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I totally thought he'd go for her,\Nwhat with how nice she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't made me any of those\Nburned cookies lately, Yoshikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, shut up. I don't burn them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kono-san made him cookies every day,\Nworked up the courage to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told him how she felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even knowing she'd be rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all I do is run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved that he's not going to date her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the possibility of him\Nnot reciprocating my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,makes me too scared to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to be the one at Tooru's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she's warm Sakura cherry blossoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I'm just gross, muddy,\Nfreezing snow, just like my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear today's gonna be\Nthe coldest day of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's gonna be this cold,\Nit could at least snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't get much snow last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was looking forward to some this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants it to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so? It's so pretty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but only in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoveling it's a huge pain,\Nand you can slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can see Miyamura slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the gross muddy snow sticks\Naround for so long. Nobody likes {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone just waits for\Nit all to melt in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snow doesn't melt just because it's spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snow melts because it\Ndecides to melt on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how badly everyone\Nwants it to stick around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the snow makes its own decision\Nto melt. That's why it melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It melts because it gets warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you think the snow melts\Nbecause the {\i1}sakura {\i0}blossoms ask it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you need to go\Nback to first-grade science.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he can say\Nall that with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so goddamn stupid, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not as stupid as you, Yoshikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the first time you've smiled all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's freezing out here. Let's head in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whose bright idea was it\Nto come up here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your hand's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really hope we get some snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pure-white kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You think Sakura got a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, only because she\Nseems a lot happier as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm off to tutoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's the exact opposite\Nof getting a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or was she talking about her not being happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sengoku-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The eraser bits on the floor were bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should let the first-years\Nhandle that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's definitely in better spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost like a weight's off her shoulders now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you should open the\Nwindow if you're going to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Remi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had tutoring today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remi always opens the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I forgot. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, did something\Nchange for you lately, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem happier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's\Nbecause something good happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hope it wasn't anything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm overthinking this, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I'm heading home.\NSorry I can't help you clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, stai, Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce s-a întâmplat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got rejected before I even\Nhad a chance to ask him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a moron. He's got to be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's the idiot who didn't want to be with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să fie exmatriculat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I ever saw\Nsomeone in my grade break down and sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only hurts more because\Nnobody's in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A început să ningă.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:09.92,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Creak...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.92,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Trembling"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.92,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Trembling"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.40,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,A wild Shindo appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.34,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"* Playing video games."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:35.04,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Until the Snow Melts"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.06,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Stare"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:35.23,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"You let this high-class meal go to waste?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.81,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"12 New Messages"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.44,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,"Hori: You're out again today. Sick?\NHope you're okay.\NMost classes were self-study today.\NLemme know if you wanna see my notes though."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.20,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,"Tooru: You getting my texts?\NYou're not picking up your phone, either.\NWe're getting worried. At least text us!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.82,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,"Hori: I had Miyamura show me how to make\Ncookies today, but my batch came out awful.\NHe ate some anyways, but ended up\Nin the bathroom for an hour... I feel bad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.33,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tooru: Kono-san told me she likes me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.05,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tooru: Kono-san told me she likes me."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:01.75,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"FLOP"
